      "body" : "I also prefer to use the @Rule, because this way I can test for expected message or cause or other stuff pertaining to the exception. For checking the cause of the exception, I use: expectedException.expectCause(Mockito.sameInstance(expectedE&zwnj;&#8203;xception)) or expectedException.expectCause(Mockito.instanceOf(MyException&zwnj;&#8203;.class))  and a few others that come in handy."
