    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Unrelated to mockito, one can catch the exception and assert its properties.  To verify that the exception did happen, assert a false condition within the try block after the statement that throws the exception.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
